# Optional repo-local env/config file hydration.
#
# Format:
#   <repo-relative-target-path> <aws-secrets-manager-secret-id>
#
# Each secret's SecretString should be the raw file contents. Do not convert a
# large .env file to JSON; upload/paste it as plaintext, then map it here.
#
# Examples:
# app/.env cursor/self-hosted-workers/repos/YOUR_REPO/app.env
# services/api/.env.production cursor/self-hosted-workers/repos/YOUR_REPO/api-production.env
